@InventorySystem.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5273

### Case Study 1: Product API - Get existing product
GET {{InventorySystem.API_HostAddress}}/api/product/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Case Study 1: Product API - Get non-existing product
GET {{InventorySystem.API_HostAddress}}/api/product/99
Accept: application/json

###

### Case Study 2: Order API - Place valid order
POST {{InventorySystem.API_HostAddress}}/api/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "customerId": 1,
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 5,
  "orderDate": "2026-04-01T00:00:00Z"
}

###

### Weather Forecast (example)
GET {{InventorySystem.API_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###
